snippet: The Jets wide receiver Jeremy Kerley, who said he slightly tore his left hamstring on the first day of camp, has returned to the field.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Jets wide receiver Jeremy Kerley returns to practice after suffering a slight hamstring injury on the first day of camp; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Jets wide receiver Jeremy Kerley, who said he slightly tore his left hamstring on the first day of camp, has returned to the field.
